'''Team Four''' was a team of [[Noghri Death Commando]]s under the command of [[Mitth'raw'nuruodo/Legends|Thrawn]]. After the failure of [[Team Eight]] to capture [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]], Team Four was sent to [[Mission to Bpfassh|attempt]] their capture. Team Four was defeated at [[Bpfassh]].

